(1, 'HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U / 4GB / 1TB / Win10 ', 'Thuộc dòng Pavilion từ thương hiệu HP nổi tiếng HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU (4MF09PA) là chiếc máy tính xách tay sở hữu cấu hình Intel Core i5 Kabylake Refresh mới nhất cho sự ổn định cao, đáp ứng tốt nhu cầu sử dụng cho người dùng thiên về tác vụ học tập - văn phòng.', '\r\n<div class=\"boxArticle\">\r\n<h3>Under the Pavilion line from the brand <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-hp-compaq\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Very good HP computer, good price, with installment payment at Mobile World\">HP</a> famous&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop/hp-pavilion-15-cs0017tu-4mf09pa?clearcache=1\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU Laptop (4MF09PA)\">HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU (4MF09PA)</a> &nbsp;is a <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genuine laptops, good prices, with installments at Mobile World\">laptop</a> &nbsp;owned configured Intel Core i5 Kabylake Refresh for the latest high stability, meet the demand for users disasters About the task <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop?g=hoc-tap-van-phong\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Computer learning - Genuine office, good price, with installment payment at Mobile World\">of learning - office</a> .</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Modern design</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Form <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"laptop\">laptop</a> has a modern design but also highlights that the iridescent metallic shell, increasing the appearance of luxury. The HP 15 cs0018TU is designed for metal housing, so it is lightweight at just <strong>1.8 kgs</strong> .</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-thieket-tgdd.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Design of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-thieket-tgdd.jpg\" style=\"display:block\" title=\"Design of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Powerful Core i5 configuration</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Laptop <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-hp-compaq?g=core-i5\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HP Core i5\">HP Core i5</a> in this article using Intel chips 8th generation, RAM <strong>4 GB</strong> , HDD <strong>1 TB</strong> should be able to install and operate quite well with office applications such as Office, Photoshop (use <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/intel-hd-graphics-620-co-manh-khong-953533#uhd-620\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Intel® UHD Graphics 620\">Intel&#39;s UHD Graphics 620</a> integrated <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/intel-hd-graphics-620-co-manh-khong-953533#uhd-620\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Intel® UHD Graphics 620\">graphics will</a> also enhance the graphics capabilities of the machine.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-cauhinh-tgdd.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Configuration of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U laptop\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-cauhinh-tgdd.jpg\" style=\"display:block\" title=\"Configuration of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U laptop\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Large 15.6 inch display</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Resolution <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/man-hinh-fhd-la-gi-956294\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Full HD\">Full HD</a> sharper screen and <strong>15.6-inch</strong> increase in size workspace and entertainment for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-manhinh-tgdd.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Screen of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-manhinh-tgdd.jpg\" style=\"display:block\" title=\"Screen of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>The keyboard is easy to operate</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s convenient for you to work with numbers like teachers, accountants ...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-banphim-tgdd.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Keyboard of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-banphim-tgdd.jpg\" style=\"display:block\" title=\"Keyboard of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Multi-touch touchpad for control</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>It has <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/hoi-dap/multi-touchpad-la-gi-920569\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Smart touchpad\">a smart touchpad that</a> allows users to drag and drop, zoom in and zoom out much easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-touchpad-tgdd.jpg\" onclick=\"return false;\"><img alt=\"Touchpad of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn/Products/Images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-touchpad-tgdd.jpg\" style=\"display:block\" title=\"Touchpad of the HP Pavilion 15 cs0018TU i5 8250U\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>Ports connected</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Like the <a href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/laptop-hp-compaq\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HP laptop\">HP laptops in the</a> same segment, the HP 15 cs0018TU still supports full connectivity standards that make working or studying convenient.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a class=\"preventdefault\" href=\"https://www.thegioididong.com/images/44/174754/hp-pavilion-15-cs0018tu-4mf09pa-congketnoi-tgdd.jpg\" onclick=\"return fal